---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526392060635-9d6019884377?w=1920&q=80" alt="Cusco architecture" loading="eager" />
  </div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content container">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span>&#9733; 4.9</span> TripAdvisor
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Un refugio de lujo<br />en el corazon del<br />imperio Inca</h1>
    <div class="gold-divider"><span>&#9788;</span></div>
    <p class="hero-sub">Casa colonial del siglo XVII transformada en un hotel boutique<br />de 12 habitaciones exclusivas</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#reservar" class="btn btn-gold">Reservar</a>
      <a href="#bienvenidos" class="btn btn-outline">Explorar</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-price">Desde <strong>$180</strong> por noche</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>&#8595;</span>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 700px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(28,25,23,0.4) 0%,
      rgba(28,25,23,0.6) 50%,
      rgba(28,25,23,0.8) 100%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.6);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero-badge span {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero-content .gold-divider {
    margin: 2rem auto;
  }

  .hero-content .gold-divider::before,
  .hero-content .gold-divider::after {
    background: var(--gold);
    width: 50px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-price {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .hero-price strong {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-sub br { display: none; }
  }
</style>
